Name: MSLF IPH System Design

Caption.String: The design point parameters determine the nominal ratings of each part of the linear fresnel system. After specifying the design point parameters here, you can specify details of each component of the system on the Solar Field, Collector and Receiver, and Thermal Storage input pages.

SD_CALC_m_dot_field_des.Label: Cycle design HTF mass flow rate

SD_COPY_q_field_des_ideal.Label: Field thermal power w/ no defocus constraints

nameplate.Label: Copy of nameplate (needed for financial models)

pb_pump_coef.Label: Pumping power for HTF through power block

tshours.Label: Hours of storage at design point
